{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"toolu_014udjusAZP7if72JKgshtMX","content":"Skill \"subgraph-extractor\" completed (forked execution).\n\nResult:\nHere is the result:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"source_url\": \"https://github.com/code-423n4/2026-03-chainlink/blob/main/src/AuctionBidder.sol\",\n  \"title\": \"AuctionBidder v1.0.0 Contract\",\n  \"sub_graphs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-001\",\n      \"name\": \"constructor\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-001_constructor.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-002\",\n      \"name\": \"bid\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-002_bid.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-003\",\n      \"name\": \"auctionCallback\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-003_auctionCallback.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-004\",\n      \"name\": \"withdraw\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-004_withdraw.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-005\",\n      \"name\": \"_setAuction\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-005_setAuction.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-006\",\n      \"name\": \"_setReceiver\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-006_setReceiver.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-007\",\n      \"name\": \"supportsInterface\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-007_supportsInterface.mmd\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nSeven program graphs extracted from `AuctionBidder.sol`:\n\n- **SG-001 constructor** -- Initializes PausableWithAccessControl, sets auction, optionally sets receiver\n- **SG-002 bid** -- Core bidding flow: loads auction, branches on solution presence (encode vs pre-approve), calls auction.bid, forwards leftover assetOut to receiver\n- **SG-003 auctionCallback** -- Callback from auction contract: authenticates caller/origin, decodes and executes arbitrary calls via _multiCall, approves amountOut back to auction\n- **SG-004 withdraw** -- Admin withdraws tokens: validates non-zero destination, iterates AssetAmount array with safeTransfer\n- **SG-005 _setAuction** -- Three-gate validation: zero address check, ERC-165 interface check, duplicate value check, then stores and emits\n- **SG-006 _setReceiver** -- Duplicate value check, stores and emits (allows setting to address(0))\n- **SG-007 supportsInterface** -- ERC-165 override declaring IAuctionCallback support\n\nKey invariants captured include the re-entrant callback pattern in `bid` (INV-003/004), the dual-path approval logic (pre-approve vs callback-approve), and the access control gates on all mutating functions."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2ea8babb-cedb-4fb8-9f79-3d3a401fb404","uuid":"e43906c9-efa3-4fb1-8e96-7c612711dab9","timestamp":"2026-03-25T11:02:59.471Z","tool_use_result":{"success":true,"commandName":"subgraph-extractor","status":"forked","agentId":"a2bde14946a4bf4a3","result":"Here is the result:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"source_url\": \"https://github.com/code-423n4/2026-03-chainlink/blob/main/src/AuctionBidder.sol\",\n  \"title\": \"AuctionBidder v1.0.0 Contract\",\n  \"sub_graphs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-001\",\n      \"name\": \"constructor\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-001_constructor.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-002\",\n      \"name\": \"bid\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-002_bid.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-003\",\n      \"name\": \"auctionCallback\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-003_auctionCallback.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-004\",\n      \"name\": \"withdraw\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-004_withdraw.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-005\",\n      \"name\": \"_setAuction\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-005_setAuction.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-006\",\n      \"name\": \"_setReceiver\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-006_setReceiver.mmd\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"SG-007\",\n      \"name\": \"supportsInterface\",\n      \"mermaid_file\": \"AuctionBidder/SG-007_supportsInterface.mmd\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nSeven program graphs extracted from `AuctionBidder.sol`:\n\n- **SG-001 constructor** -- Initializes PausableWithAccessControl, sets auction, optionally sets receiver\n- **SG-002 bid** -- Core bidding flow: loads auction, branches on solution presence (encode vs pre-approve), calls auction.bid, forwards leftover assetOut to receiver\n- **SG-003 auctionCallback** -- Callback from auction contract: authenticates caller/origin, decodes and executes arbitrary calls via _multiCall, approves amountOut back to auction\n- **SG-004 withdraw** -- Admin withdraws tokens: validates non-zero destination, iterates AssetAmount array with safeTransfer\n- **SG-005 _setAuction** -- Three-gate validation: zero address check, ERC-165 interface check, duplicate value check, then stores and emits\n- **SG-006 _setReceiver** -- Duplicate value check, stores and emits (allows setting to address(0))\n- **SG-007 supportsInterface** -- ERC-165 override declaring IAuctionCallback support\n\nKey invariants captured include the re-entrant callback pattern in `bid` (INV-003/004), the dual-path approval logic (pre-approve vs callback-approve), and the access control gates on all mutating functions."}}
